TopicTitle: Does anyone have an Orion capsule I can use?

Articles.Content: I just reached the point in my program where I need to test the Orion capsule , but I cant seem to find a mod that has a final release or beta. DOes anyone here have such mod that they can point me in right direction?

NO WAY! this cant be! How did I not know about this? OMG!!! Delta 5 heavy and proposed constellation moon lander?! BULL this isnt real . Downloading now ! Even if this is real its not real! *more coughing*

Over-modded KSP = burnt computer = PC gaming is kill = No more KSP
